UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc3='Engineering allows you to construct a wide variety of useful, amazing, and just plain weird items like rifles and scopes, motorcycles, and mechanical squirrels. However, many of these are only usable by yourself or other engineers, such as special goggles, mechanical additions to belts, boots, gloves and cloaks, and flying machines.



Most raw Engineering materials are metals gathered by Mining, so the two professions pair well.



Many creations require the use of a Blacksmith Hammer; this and other necessary materials, such as gun stocks or flux, may be purchased from trade or Engineering vendors.' WHERE entry=17134; /* Text0_0: Engineering allows you to construct a wide variety of useful, amazing, and just plain weird items like rifles and scopes, motorcycles, and mechanical squirrels. However, many of these are only usable by yourself or other engineers, such as special goggles, mechanical additions to belts, boots, gloves and cloaks, and flying machines.



